Class Ranges.Comparison

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flyingspaniel.ranges.Ranges.Comparison
  • Enclosing class:
    Ranges

    public class Ranges.Comparison
extends Object
    The values to be returned by Ranges.Comparable or Ranges.Comparator Arguably these should be enums, but they are kept as ints for compatability with Comparable and Comparator Organized into an inner class for distinctness
